 FORM update_costing .

* Update Sales Order?
   IF gv_revenue_upd_flg = 'X'.
     DATA: lv_sales_order_update_success VALUE space.

     PERFORM update_sales_order CHANGING lv_sales_order_update_success.

     IF lv_sales_order_update_success NE 'X'.

       MESSAGE s036(/noveco/evm) WITH gs_qmel-vbeln.  "Sales Order & could not be updated. Variation update was not submitted.

       RETURN.
     ENDIF.
   ENDIF.

* Update Revenue and Costing?
   IF gv_revenue_upd_flg = 'X' OR gv_fcast_upd_flg = 'X' OR gv_budget_upd_flg = 'X'.

     IF gs_qmel-revenue_updated = space OR gs_qmel-fcast_updated = space OR gs_qmel-budget_updated = space.

       IF gs_qmel-date_appr IS NOT INITIAL.

         gcl_project->unlock_claim( gs_qmel-qmnum ).
         gcl_project->unlock_sales_order( gs_qmel-vbeln ).

         PERFORM variation_update
                     USING  gv_budget_upd_flg
                            gv_revenue_upd_flg
                            gv_fcast_upd_flg.
*       Read Variation Status (in case it was completed)
         gcl_project->get_claim_header( CHANGING c_qmel = gs_qmel ).

       ENDIF.
     ENDIF.

   ENDIF.

* Rejected?
   DATA ls_epm_vupd TYPE /noveco/epm_vupd.
*     is it an rejected status via /NOVECO/EPM_VUPD?
   SELECT SINGLE * FROM /noveco/epm_vupd INTO ls_epm_vupd
